<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Revision history</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Every edit creates a revision, so you can always go back:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Click the "Revisions" tab when viewing a page</li>
  <li>See all previous versions with timestamps</li>
  <li>Compare changes between versions</li>
  <li>Revert to a previous version if needed</li>
</ul>

